Matthew T. THIEL and Nikole M. Thiel, Plaintiffs/Counterdefendants-Appellees,
and
William Traywick and Marcia Traywick, Intervening Plaintiffs/Counterdefendants-Appellees,
v.
David L. GOYINGS and Helen M. Goyings, Defendants/Counterplaintiffs-Appellants. SC: 156708
COA: 333000 Supreme Court of Michigan. February 22, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of amicus curiae Modular Home Builders Association to share five minutes of appellants' oral argument time is GRANTED.
